name: MALUNGKOT NA DIWATA (LONELY FAIRY)
description: "Diwata" ("Fairy") This lonely fairy is the main guardian of the forest from the northern Luzon of Philippines. As the progress we known arise from main city to other places, infrastructure conquer the main land and from forest to premises. too many natural habitat of different animals has gone, and the Diwata (guardian of forest) cannot bid that greediness of humanity.
